## âš™ï¸ MiljÃ¸variabler

### Backend (.env i /server eller prosjektrot)

```
# Database / Server configuration
DB_USER=            # Ditt database brukernavn
DB_PASSWORD=        # Ditt database passord
DB_HOST=localhost   # Ditt database vert (standard: localhost)
DB_PORT=3306        # Ditt database portnummer
DB_NAME=            # Ditt database navn

Server_PORT=3000    # Ditt server portnummer (standard: 3000)

# Website configuration
VITE_Server_IP=http://localhost  # Server host (standard: localhost)
VITE_Server_PORT=3000            # Server port (standard: 3000)
VITE_Web_PORT=5000               # Web port (standard: 5000)
```

